                  You are paid 5% - 80% of the price as soon as we recieve the
                  items and determine the price.
                </div>
                <div
                  style={{
                    display: "flex",
                    flexDirection: "row",
                    marginTop: 20,
                    justifyContent: "center",
                    textAlign: "center"
                  }}
                >
                  <div
                    style={{
                      display: "flex",
                      flexDirection: "column",
                      width: "15vw",
                      margin: 10
                    }}
                  >
